name: Xing Xing
description: Xing Xing is a one-armed Tibetan macaque who lives in Daliang Mountain, China, and has become an internet sensation. She gained popularity due to her unique bond with a Buddhist nun and monk who have cared for her for over 15 years. Xing Xing, whose name means "star" in Chinese, was rescued and given a safe haven at the Yanghu temple after being injured in a wild boar trap.
